text: The Type 352 is a surface search radar in People's Liberation Army Navy (PLAN) service since the 1970s. It is analogous to the MR-331 Rangout radar in Russian service. ==Specifications== * I - band * 200 kW Peak power * 55 – 77 km range * Other reported names: ** SQUARE TIE ** H/LJQ352 Category:Sea radars Category:Military radars of the People's Republic of China
title: Type 352 Radar
